rphenazine, More', 'Pyrazinamide, Rifamycin, Streptomycin, Trimethoprim, Cycloserine, Rifabutin, Isoniazid, Ethambutol, Ethionamide, Pyridoxine, Pretomanid, Aminosalicylic acid', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/284593/', '[1] "Product Information. Invega (paliperidone)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals  (2022):[2] "Product Information. Invega Hafyera (paliperidone)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals  (2021):[3] "Product Information. Invega Sustenna (paliperidone)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals  (2022):[4] "Product Information. Invega Trinza (paliperidone)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals  (2022):[5] Helland A, Spigset O "Serum concentrations of paliperidone after administration of the long-acting injectable formulation." Ther Drug Monit 39 (2017):  659-62', 1767369485);
